<t-pull-down-refresh
  id="pull-down-refresh-0"
  normal-bar-height="{{200}}"
  max-bar-height="{{272}}"
  refreshTimeout="{{3000}}"
  background="#f5f5f5"
  use-loading-slot
  loading-si
  ze="60rpx"
  loading-texts="{{['下拉刷新', '松手刷新', '正在刷新', '刷新完成', '']}}"
  bindrefresh="onPullDownRefresh0"
>
  <t-loading
    loading
    slot="loading"
    error="{{error}}"
    size="38px"
    showType="icon-only"
    layout="default"
    bind:reload="toggleError"
  >
  </t-loading>
  <view class="t-pulldown-reflesh_title">PullDownRefresh 下拉刷新</view>
  <view class="t-pulldown-reflesh_desc"
    >下拉动页面帮助用户快速刷新页面信息，刷新可以是整页刷新也可以是页面的局部刷新</view
  >

  <view class="t-pulldown-reflesh_wrapper">
    <view class="t-pulldown-reflesh_wrapper-title">01 基本用法</view>
    <view class="t-pulldown-reflesh_wrapper-desc">下拉刷新大致分为顶部下拉和中间下拉</view>
    <view class="flex pulldown-reflesh_content">
      <t-skeleton
        wx:for="{{2}}"
        wx:key="index"
        row="3"
        loading-class="skeletion-item"
        row-class="skeletion-row"
        row-width="{{['340rpx', '340rpx', '218rpx']}}"
        rowHeight="{{['342rpx', '32rpx', '32rpx']}}"
      />
      <!-- <view class="text">拖拽该区域演示 顶部下拉刷新</view> -->
    </view>
  </view>
</t-pull-down-refresh>
<t-pull-down-refresh
  id="pull-down-refresh-1"
  normal-bar-height="{{200}}"
  max-bar-height="{{272}}"
  refreshTimeout="{{3000}}"
  background="white"
  use-loading-slot
  loading-size="60rpx"
